{"tid":464651,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"繼續留學定返香港做野好?","createTime":"2017-11-10T17:06:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-11T01:26:55.000Z","uid":85084,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"338f436d3eaa6e0f2ef236fe68770e2fc1d821c4","tid":464651,"uid":85084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T17:06:28.000Z","msg":"繼續留學 讀完留係果邊做自己夢想想做既工 (但果行人工低 工時長 一世做窮鬼<br />\n(PS: 岩岩讀完個一年課程 繼續留學 = 轉學校課多個課程要2年 , 小弟今年23<br />\n<br />\n番香港搵工 勝在唔洗交租 生活應該會輕鬆好多<br />\n<br />\n真係好難決擇<br />\n如果讀上去 要屋企人洗多幾十萬 就係為左做一份可以話係無乜前途既工 又好似好自私感 <br />\n<br />\n但如果返香港  可能又會係一生既遺憾<br />\n<br />\n各位點睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 繼續留學 追逐夢想 ! 窮唔緊要! 最緊要係做到自己想做既野 !<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 錢就最實際 ! 就算做唔到有錢人 但起碼生活水平唔會差 存下錢 第時有錢做乜都得啦!"},{"pid":"2cf1116572b1bdf837aec53fdcdc4582e864804f","tid":464651,"uid":740,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T22:57:52.000Z","msg":"岩你老母<br />\n字都未識打學人做嘢"},{"pid":"048e9e5aae309029b1b21300d0ff5ce585a46f1b","tid":464651,"uid":23087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T23:03:14.000Z","msg":"邊讀留學呀 印度呀？"},{"pid":"3a451cc2e1d69890a381696042ed3b4e71d7b15c","tid":464651,"uid":140241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T23:09:56.000Z","msg":"假如你留學真係日日讀書，咁番香港算啦"},{"pid":"f73e37eaf2f5d15cdc661a1eb3994c76afd71dff","tid":464651,"uid":92063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T23:11:56.000Z","msg":"咩工呀"},{"pid":"9c28b7de814a373ec582b2ef0922ddf10d23cd00","tid":464651,"uid":37501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T23:35:40.000Z","msg":"乜都唔撚講仲要學人出投票po<br />\n你條on9早d返香港咪撚哂你老豆老母錢啦"},{"pid":"6dae0ab82990c3c7f9ff1e1fcc8a48018d5a5086","tid":464651,"uid":16938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T01:26:55.000Z","msg"